          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-6071 mdt: Fix mkdir -i 1 from DNE2 client to DNE1 server",
        "message": "LU-6071 mdt: Fix mkdir -i 1 from DNE2 client to DNE1 server\n\nAfter DNE phase 2 has been added to client it sends\ncreate request to slave MDT.  DNE1-only server doesn't\nexpect request to slave MDT from client. It expects\nonly cross-mdt request from master MDT. Thus if DNE2\nclient tries to \"mkdir -i 1\" on DNE1 server, then\nLBUG happened.\n\nThis patch removes server assert. Now server returns\n-EREMOTE in case client send request to the wrong\nMDT.\n\nSigned-off-by: Artem Blagodarenko <artem_blagodarenko@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-2319\nChange-Id: Id8045f3b70448a4aa21c1c9cbcb5dc91102ac9e7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_5"
    }
  },
